{"tid":594790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真 隨機]學校如\"自願\"全級參與TSA　考評局照舊提供評估報告","createTime":"2018-03-16T06:29:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T06:16:29.000Z","uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9196e7cf6731543b61b0872b1478a5cded3a3e","tid":594790,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:29:06.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄宣布，今年復考小三TSA，但會以抽樣、不記名、不記校的方式進行，學校亦不會收到有關的評估報告。 當局會在全港小學，包括在全港直資和津貼學校，抽10%的學生參加評估。至於特殊學習需要學生和非華語學生的抽樣比例，就需要再研究。 楊潤雄說，委員會認同TSA評估有助促進教與學，因此學校如果自願全級參與評估，考評局可以向他們提供個別評估報告，但政府不會索取有關報告。 楊潤雄又表示，過去兩年看不到TSA有明顯操練，但考慮到社會仍有擔心，因此作出今次的安排。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8b551e560acc803beef131d67860a0427b46d1","tid":594790,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859e2bbd34b05063589b273c41c91ddde3b8c129","tid":594790,"uid":176090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:34:41.000Z","msg":"學生表示多謝你 又被自願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16b5283c77459a39b5e6f9207c21b6f25a296cd","tid":594790,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T07:10:33.000Z","msg":"全級自願<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a45866541759e0236f0604d82579ee3ceb3a72","tid":594790,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T07:40:53.000Z","msg":"唔果唔&quot;自願&quot;<br />\n又要自己家長信 廢事比學校處分"},{"pid":"881e004b3f206f5c5c21afa2c4fb6a0fdef39285","tid":594790,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T06:16:29.000Z","msg":"班家長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}